TY  - JOUR
AB  - A non-parametric analysis of technology, technical change, and productivity is presented in the context of cost minimizing behavior. A number of non-parametric tests concerning the existence and nature of technical change are applied to U.S. and Japanese manufacturing data. Non-parametric measures of technical change are presented.
